</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_377_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l3">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Nu als wır dem <expan>allmechtıg<ex>en</ex></expan> got ʒu lob vnd ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l4">eren . warem Crıſtenlıchem <expan>glawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu nucʒe vnd ʒu ſterkung . dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l5"><expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleẅchtıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıg<ex>mund</ex></expan> Römıſchen ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l6">vnd ʒu Beheim etc künıg <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . vnd auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l7"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den <expan>kurfürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dıenſt . dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . mıt <expan>groſſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l8">koſt vnd ſcheͣden / auch Jn das here gen Beheim geſandt haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l9"><expan>Hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> wır dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıch <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ ſıe wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l10">Vnd als vns eẅr <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchraıb</expan> / vnd neͣmlıch ʒwen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l11">benennet dıe er meynt / dıe ſeinr <expan>beſchedıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſchult <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l12">darauf <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jm ſchrıftlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> einer vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l13"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſey vnd vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> hab / daʒ er an ſeinr <expan>beſchedıgu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gancʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l14">vnſchuldıg ſey . vnd daʒ der <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> nemlıch hanns Rommık . deſ = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l15">mals <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd auch noch niht ſey . daʒ wır ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l16">niht meͣchtıg ſeyn / Vnd als er vns <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l17">ſo <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vns der ſache <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> bas erfarn vnd <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan> niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l18">fınden daʒ dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſeinr ſcheden . fürer geweſt ſeyn oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l19">ſchult <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ vns dunkt nach dem vnd auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l20">groſſe meͣnıg volks bey ewch ʒu <expan>ſlakenw<ex>er</ex>de</expan> was . vnd nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l21">dem wır dıe ſache gehandelt vnd ſeinr ſcheden niht ʒuſchıken </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l22"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft vnd <expan>vordru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> pıllıch von Jm ver = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l23">tragen ſeyn vnd ledıg ſteen Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> auch eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l24">fleıſʒ / <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>rıchten</expan> Vns ſchrıft vnd rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l25"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu erlaſſen / Meynet er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des nıht ʒutun vnd wölt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l26"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ye ſprüch ʒu vns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jm <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> freẅnt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l27">lıchs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn . vor dem <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_377_r1l28"><expan>Römiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> künıg als wır pılleıch <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> / Deẅht Jn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_378" id="188r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l1">er ʒu <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett . ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l2"><expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs rechten gern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l3"><expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / wenn wır des ermant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l4"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . weıl <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒu den er <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd bey vns anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l5"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> . on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_378_r1l6"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> agnetıs </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_377" id="187v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
